sqlite3 -header "/Users/david/workspace/claude-code-claimdb/test_dbs/formula_1.sqlite" "
SELECT r.year, r.name, 
       COUNT(*) as total_drivers,
       SUM(CASE WHEN res.time IS NOT NULL THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) as finished_drivers,
       SUM(CASE WHEN res.time IS NULL THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) as dnf_drivers
FROM races r
JOIN results res ON r.raceId = res.raceId
WHERE r.round = 1 AND r.year BETWEEN 2000 AND 2009
GROUP BY r.raceId
ORDER BY r.year;"
